{"id": 677, "genre": 1001, "title": "逛商场，你觉得最不爽的是什么？", "description": "等了两百年的直梯，再等两百年的晚餐排队。", "record_count": 8819, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183725hqFHGrgBR3nmi0IY.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-12-06T01:02:52Z", "options": [{"id": 32000, "content": "原本只想买一样，逛着逛着，就变成了什么都想买", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 340226}, {"id": 32003, "content": "不打折", "image": null, "praise_count": 47, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 236360}, {"id": 32515, "content": "一点折扣都不打，磨半天嘴皮也不顶用", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 271557}, {"id": 32771, "content": "找不到厕所在哪儿", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 346425}, {"id": 32004, "content": "吊炸天的背景音乐 进去就想出来", "image": null, "praise_count": 92, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259427}, {"id": 35332, "content": "明明穿到身上丑到爆的衣服，硬要堆着笑说很好看哪！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 370131}, {"id": 32005, "content": "逛了很久，闹肚子，营业员说店内没有厕所", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 329992}, {"id": 32263, "content": "没有室内导航", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 180138}, {"id": 32520, "content": "连个坐的地方也没有。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 345233}, {"id": 32777, "content": "推荐护肤品的导购皮肤很差，推荐化妆品的导购化妆很差。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 157109}, {"id": 32523, "content": "没有满意的衣服。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 345258}, {"id": 32012, "content": "像是在走迷宫一样~不过这不是让你再多逗留一会儿吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 223503}, {"id": 32525, "content": "逛了一天，啥都没买.....", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211816NgsLXxc0hrUfdoC5.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 151052}, {"id": 32015, "content": "贴身丫鬟 如影随行?", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 341850}, {"id": 32783, "content": "漂亮衣服到自己身上都不好看了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 346499}, {"id": 33295, "content": "穿不下", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 348041}, {"id": 32017, "content": "过于热情的服务员", "image": null, "praise_count": 76, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 203868}, {"id": 32785, "content": "礼貌回绝服务员后依旧被她跟在后面不停地问需要什么、她给介绍…没完没了。还有一种是拉着个臭脸一直跟着你什么话都不说，你看完一样东西甚至都没碰，她就要再重新摆一下，一副特别欠抽的表情！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 346455}, {"id": 32018, "content": "男士陪逛无奈   ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 239543}, {"id": 32019, "content": "去了就饿，吃饭排队，吃完就困，结局就是花好几个小时吃一顿饭然后回家", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 233385}, {"id": 34067, "content": "太贵", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 219212}, {"id": 32020, "content": "一进店里就有个人跟着你，一直跟到发现你根本不想买！", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 236309}, {"id": 32022, "content": "有些商场的卫生间是?…我觉得公共场合很不卫生…", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 341917}, {"id": 32023, "content": "周围的人智商太低", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 203001}, {"id": 34587, "content": "被顾客当做服务员", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 363143}, {"id": 32288, "content": "看看就可以了！别给我介绍！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 343494}, {"id": 32544, "content": "陪女（性）朋友，逛n个小时，她乐此不疲，而我累成狗！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 343363}, {"id": 32289, "content": "没钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 182485}, {"id": 33313, "content": "放眼望去，全是脑袋！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 311346}, {"id": 32290, "content": "停车永远那么蛋疼，路上堵了一小时到商场一看没停车位，再堵一小时回家哭去。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 327579}, {"id": 32036, "content": "厕所是马桶 简直是要命的设计 蹲坑会干净很多这么简单的道理不懂吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164498}, {"id": 32296, "content": "一个人...", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 232642}, {"id": 32297, "content": "找不到厕所?，找到了还等好久", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 343631}, {"id": 32045, "content": "音乐太吵", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 306521}, {"id": 60720, "content": "女厕所的人永远那么多", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 528763}, {"id": 32049, "content": "找不到进来时的入口", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 324824}, {"id": 32305, "content": "你们说呢？！?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 343691}, {"id": 34353, "content": "真的希望所有商场（除餐饮）都像个超市，“热情”的服务员奏凯", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 349587}, {"id": 32050, "content": "售货员老是在不停的说话，他们还不知道我要什么，而且不在推荐产品的时候提一提价钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 124369}, {"id": 32306, "content": "你们说呢？！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 343691}, {"id": 32052, "content": "商场是啥？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 342178}, {"id": 32309, "content": "洗手间环境差 \r\n只有一处直达电梯 （是的 就有这样的购物中心 还是观光电梯）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 299843}, {"id": 32054, "content": "平时太低调，结果白金卡都不好意思在土豪狂拽酷面前拿出来…", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211822CguFJmI7TkBh5wn4.jpg", "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 342174}, {"id": 40758, "content": "人太多，声音嘈杂，广播放难听的歌", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 419663}, {"id": 32057, "content": "看服务员脸色", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 341216}, {"id": 35385, "content": "陪女性逛，走了十几条街的商场她们才有灵感要买什么，男的永远累趴，每次进店女的看衣服男的永远在找凳子，见到凳子感觉好淘到宝。?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 281714}, {"id": 34106, "content": "排队排队还有人插队", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 314948}, {"id": 32059, "content": "身材不够好", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 342226}, {"id": 32060, "content": "周围都是人，只有我一条（单身）狗。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 328264}, {"id": 33085, "content": "看中的太贵，但要找理由走掉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 348163}]}